EU Rules on Securities Markets, Insider Trading Set for Oct. 20

-- B y   J i m   B r u n s d e n
-- 
2011-10-07T10:15:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-07/eu-rules-on-securities-markets-insider-trading-set-for-oct-20.html
The European Commission will present
proposals on Oct. 20 to toughen rules for trading on financial
markets in the 27-nation region.  It will also present measures to better tackle market
manipulation and insider dealing, it said on its website today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jim Brunsden in Brussels at 
